sequenceDiagram
    participant App as My App
    participant AI as GPT Model
    participant Tool as External Tool

    App->>AI: Tool list + user question
    AI->>AI: Decide which tool is needed
    AI-->>App: "Run get_weather('Seoul')"
    App->>Tool: Execute get_weather('Seoul')
    Tool-->>App: 25°C, Clear
    App->>AI: Send execution result
    AI-->>App: "Seoul is 25°C and clear"
